You can find the source code of the individual tools by following the URLs below.

GPGMail:
https://gpgtools.org/source/gpgmail
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGMail

GPG Keychain Access:
https://gpgtools.org/source/gka
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGKeychainAccess

GPGPreferences:
https://gpgtools.org/source/gpgpreferences
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGPreferences

GPGServices:
https://gpgtools.org/source/gpgservices
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGServices

Libmacgpg:
https://gpgtools.org/source/libmacgpg
https://github.com/GPGTools/Libmacgpg

MacGPG2:
https://gpgtools.org/source/macgpg2
https://github.com/GPGTools/MacGPG2

Installer:
https://gpgtools.org/source/installer
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGTools_installer

GPGTools_Core:
https://gpgtools.org/source/core
https://github.com/GPGTools/GPGTools_Core

Sparkle:
https://gpgtools.org/source/sparkle
https://github.com/GPGTools/Sparkle


